Together, <font color="#C0C0C0"><em>unite, unite, Europe</em></font></p>
<p>With you, so far and different<br />
With you, a friend that I thought I lost<br />
You and I, having the same dream<br />
Together, <font color="#C0C0C0"><em>unite, unite, Europe</em></font></p>
<p>And for you, a woman without borders<br />
With you, under the same flags<br />
You and I, under the same sky<br />
Together, <font color="#C0C0C0"><em>unite, unite, Europe</em></font></p>
<p>We&#8217;re more and more free<br />
It&#8217;s no longer a dream and you&#8217;re no longer alone<br />
We&#8217;re higher and higher<br />
Give me your hand, so we can fly</p>
<p>Europe is not far away<br />
This is an Italian song for you<br />
